# Wiring diagram notes


Key connections:
- Battery (XT60) → PDB → ESCs → Motors
- PDB → Holybro PM06 → Pixhawk 2.4.8 (5V rail)
- GPS (M8N) connected to GPS port with compass wiring
- Telemetry radio UART to TELEM1
- Safety switch and buzzer to AUX


Safety notes:
- Balance-charge LiPo only; never charge unattended.
- Secure all wiring with zip ties and apply threadlocker to metal fasteners.
